// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0668 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 7cd124d6-9a80-55c1-90bf-8e219a90f73d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:24.04*")
